issue_description.code_example:
```tsx
// File: demo/src/components/elements/gradient-border-wrapper.tsx, Lines 115-127
// BUG: The same wrapper element owns both classes, so the descendant hover selector below does not match it.
className={clsx(
'gradient-border-wrapper gradient-border-rotating relative inline-flex',
className
)}
style={{
'--gradient-rotation-duration': `${rotationDuration}ms`,
padding: `${GRADIENT_CONFIG.borderWidth}px`,
borderRadius: '9999px',
animationPlayState: isVisible ? 'running' : 'paused',
} as CSSProperties}
```

```css
/* File: demo/src/app/globals.css, Lines 1154-1157 */
/* BUG: This selector expects .gradient-border-rotating to be a descendant, not the hovered wrapper itself. */
.gradient-border-wrapper:hover .gradient-border-rotating,
.gradient-border-wrapper:hover .gradient-border-glow {
animation-duration: calc(var(--gradient-rotation-duration) * 0.5);
}
```
